sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant M as Master CommitLog
    participant F as Flush Service
    participant H as HAService
    participant S as Slave CommitLog

    P->>M: SendMessage
    M->>M: 追加消息，得到 nextOffset
    par 本机刷盘
        M->>F: 提交 GroupCommitRequest(nextOffset)
        F-->>M: flushedWhere >= nextOffset
    and 副本复制
        M->>H: 提交 HA GroupCommitRequest(nextOffset, ackNums)
        H->>S: 推送 offset + bodySize + CommitLog bytes
        S->>S: 按相同物理位点追加
        S-->>H: 上报 slaveMaxOffset
        H-->>M: ACK 数量达到要求
    end
    M-->>P: 汇总 flushStatus 与 replicaStatus
